  "recommended_next_step": "Prepare CONTINUITY_REPORT_SYNTHESIS_IMPLEMENTATION_REVIEW_V1 before writing code, verifying that pure-function synthesis can produce deterministic in-memory reports from explicit artifacts without IO, mutation, authority expansion, orchestration, persistence, or semantic autonomy."
